    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This iridescent, black *+2 striking shock thundering fighting fan* is crafted from the crackling feathers of thunderbirds to resemble one of the beast\u2019s mighty wings. Channeling the avian\u2019s tempestuous nature, you are surrounded by a stormy shell of wind and electricity while wielding a storm herald, granting you resistance 5 to electricity and sonic damage.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
          "alternate_type": "legacy",
          "aonid": 159,
          "game-obj": "Traits",
          "type": "alternate_link"
